Encoder class
Instance variables:
1. private String originalMessage -> message before encryption
Constructors:
1. public Encoder(String originalMessage)
   Initialize the private String variable originalMessage to the value of the parameter.
Methods:
1. public String atbashEncoder()
   Initialize the String encryptedMessage as an empty String.
   Initialize the array originalLetters with all the letters in uppercase in alphabetical order for the elements.
   Initialize the array encryptedLetters with all the letters in uppercase in the reverse of alphabetical order for the elements.
   Use a for loop with the initialization int index = 0, the test condition index is less than the length of the String originalMessage, and the increment of 1 to index every loop.
      Initialize the String letter as the substring of the String originalMessage with the beginning index as index and the end index as index plus 1.
      Initialize the int arrayIndex to 0.


Decoder class
Instance variables:
1. private String originalMessage -> message before decryption
Constructors:
1. public Decoder(String originalMessage)
   Initialize the private String variable original Message to the value of the parameter.